â”‚
â”œâ”€â”€ AI                    # API access (ChatGPT, Gemini)
â”œâ”€â”€ Advanced_Maths        # Arithmetic, algebra, statistics
â”œâ”€â”€ Calculus              # Symbolic calculus and differentiation
â”œâ”€â”€ Chemistry             # Periodic table and constants
â”œâ”€â”€ Converter             # File format converters
â”œâ”€â”€ Database              # SQLite handler
â”œâ”€â”€ Media                 # Audio, video, and image tools
â”œâ”€â”€ Matrices, Vectors     # Linear algebra utilities
â”œâ”€â”€ NeuraPython_ML        # Scikit-learn unified wrapper
â”œâ”€â”€ NeuralNetwork         # TensorFlow / PyTorch integration
â”œâ”€â”€ Physics               # Mechanics, relativity, quantum
â”œâ”€â”€ Reader                # File readers (txt, pdf, json, etc.)
â”œâ”€â”€ Visualizer2D / 3D     # Graph plotting
â”œâ”€â”€ WebServer             # Flask API server
